<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.93.10039.figure13>
    dc:description "Figure 13. Nassa munda Sturany, 1900, Station 135 (Akik Seghir, Eritrea, Red Sea). A-C, E. Figured syntype, NHMW 84190: front (A), right side (B), back (C), protoconch (E). D. Original figure by Sturany (1903). F. Original label of figured syntype. Scale bars: A-C: 2 mm, E: 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118650" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

